13:47.427 --> 13:51.229
- [chop]
- [squealing]

13:57.037 --> 13:58.970
- [chop]
- [squealing]

14:00.941 --> 14:03.241
[squealing]

15:18.018 --> 15:19.450
- [chop]
- [squeals]

16:02.028 --> 16:04.529
