16:49.075 --> 16:50.608
I'm pretty, pretty rich.

16:50.610 --> 16:53.478
- Five million.
- Not that rich.

16:53.480 --> 16:56.514
$500,000.
Half a million.

16:57.684 --> 17:00.251
- Two million.
- One.

17:06.092 --> 17:07.592
Why did you chop her tail off?

17:08.595 --> 17:10.294
[splash]

17:19.372 --> 17:23.307
