17:40.527 --> 17:41.592
[click]

17:42.529 --> 17:43.594
[click]

17:44.531 --> 17:45.596
[click]

17:57.677 --> 17:58.743
[yelps]

18:31.211 --> 18:33.611
[gasping]

18:34.581 --> 18:36.547
[squealing]

19:08.248 --> 19:10.348
[metal creaking]

19:11.751 --> 19:16.554
[seagulls cawing]

19:17.490 --> 19:20.224
[dog barking]

19:20.226 --> 19:23.628
<i> ¶¶ ['50s oldies]</i>

19:25.665 --> 19:29.700
<i> [TV playing]</i>

19:45.652 --> 19:50.454
The tongue of a blue whale
can be as large as a Volkswagen.

19:50.456 --> 19:52.323
[giggles]

19:52.325 --> 19:53.724
You know what that means.

19:53.726 --> 19:55.726
Hey, guys, let me
get in on this.

19:55.728 --> 19:57.662
Good form today, Martha-Rose.

19:57.664 --> 19:59.397
Thank you, Reyna.

20:00.400 --> 20:02.466
Can I play?

20:02.468 --> 20:03.868
Can I play this time?

20:04.537 --> 20:07.338
You guys, hey, come on,
let me get in on this.

20:07.340 --> 20:10.841
Go check the scores on the
Olympics and then you can play.

20:10.843 --> 20:12.877
And see if they're saying
when men's swimming starts!

20:13.813 --> 20:16.314
You know, June, you could
ask your imaginary friend

20:16.316 --> 20:18.382
to steal some uppers for us.

20:18.551 --> 20:21.586
You know, since no one
sees her but you.

20:24.290 --> 20:26.457
I really like the coffee here.
Freshly ground.

20:26.459 --> 20:28.926
Was there an old insane asylum
here or something?

20:28.928 --> 20:30.428
What are those pictures?

20:30.430 --> 20:32.463
Way before all this
suburban development.

20:32.465 --> 20:35.866
Doc probably thought it'd be
apropos to have his home here

20:35.868 --> 20:37.301
for the disturbed.

20:40.807 --> 20:43.374
Hallowed ground
to a history buff.

20:44.744 --> 20:47.778
You know, it actually
still exists.

20:49.782 --> 20:51.515
Right beneath us.

20:54.454 --> 20:55.519
Right beneath us.

20:57.523 --> 20:59.690
They didn't seal it

20:59.691 --> 21:01.858
'cause it adds value to
the house if it has a cellar.

21:01.861 --> 21:03.294
What the fuck was that?

21:10.970 --> 21:12.770
Yeah, you're supposed
to go change that bulb.

21:17.810 --> 21:19.777
[distant squealing]

21:28.888 --> 21:34.659
Hey, so behind one of
these doors in this house

21:34.661 --> 21:39.630
are steps that go down
to the weirdest basement

21:39.632 --> 21:41.399
in the New World.

21:43.970 --> 21:45.903
That's not a real
statistic though.

21:47.874 --> 21:48.939
Which door is it?

21:53.846 --> 21:56.580
<i> ¶¶ [ominous]</i>

22:00.486 --> 22:02.053
Hey, light bulb.

22:11.931 --> 22:12.997
That's Coffee's.

22:12.999 --> 22:14.665
His girlfriend hates guns,

22:14.667 --> 22:16.734
so he keeps it here.

22:19.772 --> 22:21.839
Doc does the same thing
with his gun.

22:23.543 --> 22:24.542
Weird.

22:55.842 --> 22:57.742
[walkie-talkie chatter]

22:59.912 --> 23:01.846
[laughing]

23:02.982 --> 23:06.083
[mermaid squeals]

23:06.085 --> 23:09.387
June, June, I think there's
a ghost in the bathroom!

23:10.089 --> 23:11.689
Guys, shut up!

23:11.691 --> 23:13.491
I think there's something
in the bathroom.

23:14.861 --> 23:17.128
[giggling]

23:20.900 --> 23:22.867
Girls.

23:22.869 --> 23:24.668
Girls!

23:24.670 --> 23:28.839
Girls, do not engage
June's fantasy!

23:37.083 --> 23:39.683
[growling]

23:43.956 --> 23:46.490
Oh, it is the new girl.

23:46.492 --> 23:47.958
And all of you
acting like this

23:47.960 --> 23:51.495
is not gonna make her feel
very at home, is it?

23:51.497 --> 23:53.731
Now, come on,
back in the room, come on.

23:53.733 --> 23:56.167
We just wanted--
We were just saying hi.

23:57.770 --> 23:59.036
Good girls, come on.

23:59.038 --> 24:01.172
I wasn't gonna hurt her.

25:16.115 --> 25:19.884
[mermaid squealing]

25:28.060 --> 25:30.828
[mermaid squealing]

26:06.666 --> 26:09.934
[metal tinkling]

26:11.203 --> 26:14.171
[snarls, squeals]

26:15.741 --> 26:18.242
[splashing]

26:18.244 --> 26:19.843
GHOST GIRL: Her legs don't work.

26:19.845 --> 26:20.911
Is she paralyzed?

26:21.847 --> 26:23.213
No wheelchair.

26:23.215 --> 26:25.149
Think they're
encouraging her to walk?

26:25.151 --> 26:27.318
Got it.
She's in denial, like you.

26:27.320 --> 26:29.853
Gonna steal a wheelchair.

26:29.855 --> 26:31.855
They don't lock
the storage closet.

26:31.857 --> 26:33.223
Even if it were locked,

26:33.225 --> 26:35.859
why not just walk
through the door?

26:35.861 --> 26:37.761
Do you ever wonder why you
can't seem to touch anyone,

26:37.763 --> 26:40.064
- but you can open cabinets?
- What are you talking about?

26:40.066 --> 26:41.932
Look, you were here
ten years ago,

26:41.934 --> 26:44.068
but you're certainly
not here now.

26:44.070 --> 26:46.937
You can't walk through walls,
through doors.

26:46.939 --> 26:49.239
You're not one of us.

26:49.241 --> 26:51.208
Will you shut the fuck up?

26:51.210 --> 26:53.277
[laughing]

27:04.890 --> 27:07.324
<i> ¶¶ [ominous]</i>

27:46.298 --> 27:49.133
[tinkling]

27:49.135 --> 27:51.035
<i> ¶¶ [cartoony]</i>

27:57.810 --> 27:59.977
[walkie-talkie chatter]

27:59.979 --> 28:02.012
[clatter]

28:05.351 --> 28:09.219
<i> ¶¶ [mysterious]</i>

28:12.258 --> 28:14.091
[walkie-talkie static]

29:02.374 --> 29:06.844
<i> ¶¶ [Muzak]</i>

29:06.846 --> 29:10.948
Rabbit? Do I see the bunnies?
Where are they?

29:10.950 --> 29:12.950
[giggling]

29:12.952 --> 29:16.253
WOMAN: <i> There's fresh coffee</i>
<i> in the kitchen. Reyna?</i>

29:18.190 --> 29:19.473
WOMAN ON SPEAKER: <i> Medication.</i>

29:19.474 --> 29:20.757
Did you guys hear
the dog again last night?

29:21.827 --> 29:23.360
Can we not talk
about that, Alex?

29:25.364 --> 29:28.298
Guys, what is the wheelchair
doing in this room?

29:28.300 --> 29:32.503
Girls, where are the fish?
Don't we have more fish?

29:34.840 --> 29:36.240
SUSAN: And the admission
processing board

29:36.242 --> 29:37.441
have inquired about
the new patient.

29:37.443 --> 29:39.343
You haven't
filed anything yet.

29:39.345 --> 29:42.112
Just tell them we're working on
the paperwork, ran out of forms.

29:42.114 --> 29:44.114
You have oodles of messages
from the safety inspector

29:44.116 --> 29:45.849
wanting to seal off
that entrance downstairs.

29:45.851 --> 29:47.050
I'm working down there.

29:47.052 --> 29:48.252
Turning the old asylum
into a museum.

29:48.254 --> 29:49.987
[phone ringing]

29:49.989 --> 29:51.922
There's a perfectly
good lock on the door.

29:51.924 --> 29:53.290
He says a locked door
isn't enough.

29:53.292 --> 29:56.126
Assholes just need something
to complain about.

30:00.266 --> 30:01.465
Beyer Mental Health.
This is Susan.

30:01.467 --> 30:02.766
<i> WOMAN: Hi, I have a question.</i>

30:02.767 --> 30:04.066
<i> My daughter</i>
<i> just got out of rehab,</i>

30:04.069 --> 30:06.970
<i> - and I was wondering--</i>
- Yes, we...

30:07.406 --> 30:08.939
Are you gonna join us today?

30:10.009 --> 30:12.276
Okay, suit yourself.

30:12.278 --> 30:14.011
The men's swimming matches
are on.

30:14.013 --> 30:16.914
Sandra, maybe I should
bring her breakfast in here?

30:16.916 --> 30:19.149
- Men in Speedos!
- Okay.

30:19.151 --> 30:21.351
Men with big muscles!

30:21.353 --> 30:24.354
Don't bother replying.
It's only a mental home.

30:24.356 --> 30:26.256
We're all clearly secure
with ourselves.

30:27.226 --> 30:29.159
[grunts]

30:29.161 --> 30:30.227
Was that you?

30:34.133 --> 30:35.199
Are you okay?

30:51.116 --> 30:52.516
What are you looking at?

31:02.094 --> 31:05.162
- [squeals]
- Hey, hey, hey, hey.

31:05.164 --> 31:07.965
Look what I got.
Look what I got right here.

31:07.967 --> 31:10.167
Come on, come on.

31:10.169 --> 31:13.070
Shh. Shh.

31:13.072 --> 31:14.137
Easy.

31:15.074 --> 31:18.141
Look what I have got
for you, huh?

31:20.079 --> 31:24.081
Hey, don't these
look like toys?

31:25.184 --> 31:26.550
Pretty, huh?

31:27.553 --> 31:29.486
Very pretty.

31:30.956 --> 31:32.456
Do you like those?

31:32.458 --> 31:34.558
Look at this.
Would you like to...

31:35.494 --> 31:37.394
What do you think about him?

31:40.032 --> 31:42.566
You don't have to be afraid.

31:45.170 --> 31:48.171
Ooh, that one smells
like a fish tank.

31:48.173 --> 31:50.540
What do you think, huh?
You can touch it.

31:50.542 --> 31:54.044
You can play with this
if you wanted to.

32:22.441 --> 32:25.042
Oh, my God.

32:25.044 --> 32:27.444
You know sign language.

32:40.159 --> 32:42.125
[camera clicking]

32:45.564 --> 32:48.332
