a free sandwich.

37:52.337 --> 37:54.537
MILLER: She learned
to sign from--

37:54.539 --> 37:55.839
- Pirates.
- Pirates.

37:55.841 --> 37:57.474
Her and her species.

37:57.476 --> 37:58.742
But the men became--

37:58.744 --> 38:01.811
What are you saying?
What is this word?

38:01.813 --> 38:03.380
Aggressive?

38:03.382 --> 38:05.482
- Aggressive.
- Fucking pirates.

38:05.484 --> 38:10.754
And the men stole her species
from the sea generations ago.

38:10.756 --> 38:15.358
Thousands of girls
who were born on land

38:15.360 --> 38:17.727
are walking around...

38:17.729 --> 38:20.363
with no idea that...

38:20.365 --> 38:22.932
their genes go back to this...

38:22.934 --> 38:25.735
ocean resident?

38:25.737 --> 38:27.404
Like a fish?

38:27.406 --> 38:28.938
I don't understand.

38:28.940 --> 38:31.374
I don't know
what she's trying to say.

38:31.376 --> 38:34.544
Dr. Miller, I think
she thinks she's a mermaid.

38:35.514 --> 38:38.415
Why is she, um...

38:38.417 --> 38:41.551
