38:42.954 --> 38:46.423
She's saying it happens...

38:46.425 --> 38:48.458
when she's forced to dry land,

38:48.460 --> 38:52.962
or when her tail is
removed from her body.

38:53.965 --> 38:55.999
They completely blend...

38:56.001 --> 38:59.002
into full humans.

39:02.841 --> 39:04.874
What is this?
What are you saying?

39:04.876 --> 39:06.943
- [grunting]
- What does this mean?

39:10.882 --> 39:12.615
You're dying.

39:15.687 --> 39:17.587
You're dying?

39:17.589 --> 39:20.557
Some who are like her
can survive on land,

39:20.559 --> 39:22.592
but many don't.

39:25.030 --> 39:26.730
She says she's gonna die

39:26.732 --> 39:30.433
if she doesn't get back
to the ocean soon.

39:30.435 --> 39:32.669
SANDRA: Okay, that's enough
for tonight, ladies.

39:32.671 --> 39:34.704
Everybody to your
sleeping quarters.

39:34.706 --> 39:36.005
Gonna give your medications
there tonight.

39:36.007 --> 39:38.842
Come on, everybody up.
We're done.

39:38.844 --> 39:41.644
Come on.
That's enough for tonight.

39:41.646 --> 39:43.113
Time to go.

39:44.750 --> 39:47.584
I don't want any horsing around
tonight either.

39:47.586 --> 39:49.786
Reyna, that means you too.

39:57.763 --> 39:58.928
Reyna!

39:58.930 --> 40:00.964
Fuck you, mermaid.

40:00.966 --> 40:02.732
Reyna!

40:02.734 --> 40:05.568
Sorry, Sandra!

40:05.570 --> 40:08.605
I'm ready for
my antipsychotic now!

40:08.607 --> 40:10.974
