that Dr. Miller...

40:10.976 --> 40:14.511
rectally administer the pill
into me tonight?

40:14.513 --> 40:15.745
Reyna!

40:15.747 --> 40:18.681
Please, nurse?
[laughs]

40:32.063 --> 40:34.764
I think I would be
from mermaids.

40:34.766 --> 40:37.767
I don't know. I just think
I'd be a mermaid.

