blow-up pool in the backyard.

40:41.540 --> 40:42.939
Therefore,
you must be a mermaid.

40:42.941 --> 40:46.009
- Shut up, Edith Post.
- Emily Post.

40:46.011 --> 40:48.044
All I'm saying is if one of us
was a fucking mermaid

40:48.046 --> 40:49.112
