40:49.114 --> 40:50.513
I'd be the fucking mermaid.

40:50.515 --> 40:51.815
You definitely smell like one.

40:51.817 --> 40:53.817
What do you think, June?

40:53.819 --> 40:56.886
Better yet, let's ask
June's imaginary friend

40:56.888 --> 40:59.689
