about all this.

40:59.691 --> 41:01.124
Huh, June?

41:07.098 --> 41:08.164
Hmm.

41:09.568 --> 41:10.967
That's what I thought.

41:12.704 --> 41:14.804
How about you put this
over your face

41:14.806 --> 41:16.105
so I can stop looking at it?

41:16.107 --> 41:17.540
[thunderclap]

41:17.542 --> 41:19.542
Put it over your head!

41:19.544 --> 41:22.078
Put it over
your fucking head!

41:22.080 --> 41:24.547
[whimpering]

41:24.549 --> 41:26.916
You're so fucking useless.
Are you happy, newbie?

41:26.918 --> 41:28.852
This is what happens
when you turn this place

41:28.854 --> 41:31.621
into a house of lies.

41:31.623 --> 41:33.056
Mermaid, my ass.

41:33.058 --> 41:35.725
Why don't you go to hell,
you little faker?

41:35.727 --> 41:37.060
I believe you.

41:37.062 --> 41:38.561
ALEX: I think I'm going
start telling people

41:38.563 --> 41:40.063
I'm actually a mermaid princess,

41:40.065 --> 41:43.166
so I don't have to deal
with reality either.

41:48.607 --> 41:49.772
[gasps]

41:58.717 --> 41:59.916
GHOST GIRL: I don't understand.

42:08.793 --> 42:10.026
Ugh! Fuck!

42:11.796 --> 42:13.930
[electricity crackling]

42:27.112 --> 42:29.045
GUARD: She chipped my tooth.

42:30.849 --> 42:35.084
Doc, doesn't this lead
to the lower asylum?

42:37.222 --> 42:39.756
- I thought it was closed off.
- It is.

42:40.725 --> 42:41.758
Now it isn't.

42:41.760 --> 42:44.627
This patient requires isolation.

42:44.629 --> 42:47.130
You're more than welcome
to come down and help me

42:47.132 --> 42:49.699
or stay up here
if you're afraid.

42:49.701 --> 42:51.634
Yeah.

42:51.636 --> 42:54.137
I can't go down there.

42:54.139 --> 42:58.741
Do you need me to help,
or can you do this by yourself?

42:58.743 --> 43:01.210
Because I--

43:01.212 --> 43:05.148
<i> ¶¶ [sinister]</i>

43:19.064 --> 43:21.798
Do you think it's right to put
a girl down there in the dark?

43:21.800 --> 43:25.802
I mean, isn't that
gonna be traumatic?

43:25.804 --> 43:28.871
Does it look like
I have a PhD?

43:31.810 --> 43:33.810
I would have gone down there
if I had a drink.

43:33.812 --> 43:35.979
I mean, all I need
is one drink.

43:35.981 --> 43:38.114
Oh, definitely.
Me too.

43:38.116 --> 43:41.751
If I had a margarita first,
then no problem.

43:41.753 --> 43:45.054
[water dripping]

43:46.257 --> 43:48.257
[gas hissing]

43:53.064 --> 43:54.797
Goddamn it.

44:18.323 --> 44:20.256
Where do you think
they took her?

44:20.258 --> 44:23.126
I don't know, but someone's
gotta go look, bring back intel.

44:23.128 --> 44:25.128
Becky, don't say intel.
It's irritating.

44:25.130 --> 44:26.796
You're gonna help her,
aren't you?

44:26.798 --> 44:29.098
No, but you can,
if you want.

44:30.235 --> 44:33.102
[panting]

44:33.104 --> 44:35.171
LINDA: I'll go find her.

44:35.173 --> 44:39.275
If anyone sees you after hours,
you'll get quarantined, Linda.

44:39.277 --> 44:42.011
Kinda goes without saying,
Charlotte.

44:56.261 --> 44:59.062
I told you not to give away
our secret, tadpole.

45:12.310 --> 45:15.078
<i> ¶¶ [suspense]</i>

45:32.964 --> 45:34.197
[gasps]

45:37.168 --> 45:39.402
I-- The girls,
they wanted me to--

45:39.404 --> 45:44.040
Go ahead.
She's right down there.

45:48.880 --> 45:50.947
Do you have
an extension cord?

45:58.857 --> 45:59.956
[door closes]

46:24.883 --> 46:27.283
GHOST GIRL: Linda! Linda!

46:27.285 --> 46:29.051
We're in here!

46:29.053 --> 46:30.953
Linda!

46:30.955 --> 46:32.455
Linda, we're in here!

46:32.457 --> 46:35.124
Look at me!
Look at me, Linda!

46:35.126 --> 46:36.993
We're in here!

46:36.995 --> 46:38.427
You looked right at me.

46:54.145 --> 46:55.211
[screams]

46:55.213 --> 46:57.013
Please stop!
[grunts]

47:19.304 --> 47:23.139
[labored breathing]

47:27.011 --> 47:28.110
I can't--

47:37.322 --> 47:39.322
I can't see.

47:39.324 --> 47:41.390
What am I sitting on?
What--

47:43.394 --> 47:46.429
[panting]

47:46.431 --> 47:49.232
[growling]

47:54.072 --> 47:56.305
Okay, give me a wall.

47:57.475 --> 47:59.041
Where's the wall?

48:03.548 --> 48:05.381
Come on, where's the fucking--

48:05.383 --> 48:07.283
[growling]

48:20.298 --> 48:24.367
[growling]

48:26.070 --> 48:28.037
Who's gonna get
a new squeaky toy tomorrow?

48:28.039 --> 48:30.373
[distant screaming]

48:31.576 --> 48:33.442
Too scary.

48:33.444 --> 48:36.212
Too scary. Can't breathe.

48:36.214 --> 48:39.015
Turn-- Turn the lights, please!

48:39.017 --> 48:40.483
I don't like the dark.

49:05.043 --> 49:07.276
June kept the room lit up all
night, so I wouldn't be scared.

49:07.278 --> 49:09.145
You're not making any sense.

49:09.147 --> 49:12.181
I think it's bioluminescence.
Like the deep sea fish

49:12.183 --> 49:14.083
with the little light
in front of their sharp teeth

49:14.085 --> 49:16.519
that attracts
little fishies to them,

49:16.521 --> 49:19.388
lures smaller fish to her,
so she can eat them.

49:19.390 --> 49:21.023
June, in the living room.

49:21.025 --> 49:22.091
Have you seen Linda
and the new girl?

49:22.093 --> 49:23.159
No, ask her.

49:38.309 --> 49:40.209
BEYER:
You're a goddamn survivor.

49:40.211 --> 49:43.379
<i> ¶¶ ["Theme from</i> Bonanza"]

49:49.320 --> 49:54.323
<i> ¶¶ [continues]</i>

49:59.263 --> 50:01.163
[giggling]

50:02.100 --> 50:03.466
That's cool.

50:03.468 --> 50:06.135
[grunting]

50:09.474 --> 50:12.675
Are you understanding this?

50:21.519 --> 50:27.223
<i> [TV playing]</i>

50:27.225 --> 50:31.360
Don't tell anyone I do this.

50:31.362 --> 50:33.229
It doesn't look good.

50:37.235 --> 50:39.368
Secret smoker.

50:43.341 --> 50:45.141
- Told ya.
- What?

50:45.143 --> 50:48.110
- We're not talking to you.
- What?

50:48.112 --> 50:51.380
I'm not talking to you.

50:57.422 --> 51:01.123
I'm telling you
something's wrong.

51:01.125 --> 51:02.391
BEYER: Test for acuity.

51:02.393 --> 51:03.659
- Eye test? Come on.
- Please, Margaret.

51:12.236 --> 51:14.503
Step back, Miller.
Don't help her.

51:58.382 --> 51:59.482
[snap]

52:17.301 --> 52:18.534
[grunts]

52:24.342 --> 52:26.809
I ordered this for Linda.

52:28.312 --> 52:29.378
Jesus.

52:29.380 --> 52:32.381
Oh, this is very inappropriate.

52:35.820 --> 52:39.221
I didn't realize
how kinky this was.

52:39.223 --> 52:41.657
Don't wear this
in front of security.

52:51.802 --> 52:55.604
Hey, have you seen
the new girl?

52:55.606 --> 52:58.274
You lost her?

52:58.276 --> 52:59.642
[chuckles]

52:59.644 --> 53:01.710
Yeah, kind of.
A little bit.

53:01.712 --> 53:03.345
She just sort of
wandered off.

53:03.347 --> 53:04.747
Are you smoking in here?

53:04.749 --> 53:07.349
- I've been smoking like a fish.
- Like a chimney.

53:07.351 --> 53:09.552
What did I say?

53:09.554 --> 53:12.254
Anyway, if you see her
on the monitor, let me know.

53:12.256 --> 53:14.390
I stopped looking at it
when you covered it

53:14.392 --> 53:17.259
with your grandma sweater.

53:17.261 --> 53:20.696
Okay, if you could take a peek
at it and see if you see her.

53:20.698 --> 53:23.599
