on these monitors.

53:23.601 --> 53:25.601
I know that.

53:44.689 --> 53:46.789
There you are,
little slippery one.

53:47.858 --> 53:49.525
Come on.

53:49.527 --> 53:51.694
Hey, guys,
she's pointing at something.

53:51.696 --> 53:53.429
I think it's Charlotte's book.

53:53.431 --> 53:55.564
[laughing]
Oh, no.

53:55.566 --> 53:57.700
