the same trashy novel

53:57.702 --> 53:59.435
for about two years now.

53:59.437 --> 54:01.437
I would not expect
to borrow it.

54:01.439 --> 54:03.439
[dog barking]

54:11.315 --> 54:12.881
[engine revs]

54:12.883 --> 54:14.683
Whoa. What is new girl
wearing?

54:14.685 --> 54:16.585
[laughing]

54:26.364 --> 54:27.563
[thud]

54:28.866 --> 54:32.534
<i> ¶¶ [brisk]</i>

54:39.877 --> 54:42.478
[phone ringing]

54:42.480 --> 54:43.712
I can get that
at the nurses' station.

54:43.714 --> 54:45.547
I was just using the potty.

54:47.485 --> 54:50.686
<i> - ¶¶ [continues]</i>
- [Reyna howling]

54:54.625 --> 54:55.758
I hear water!

54:55.760 --> 54:58.360
- I hear the water!
- I hear it too!

54:58.362 --> 54:59.795
It's the river!

55:03.668 --> 55:05.768
Holy shit.
It's beautiful!

55:05.770 --> 55:07.770
How much of this do you think
is sewage runoff?

55:07.772 --> 55:11.607
[howling]

55:19.383 --> 55:20.916
Look at Becky!

55:20.918 --> 55:23.519
Just go in your underwear
like it's a bathing suit.

55:23.521 --> 55:25.721
No. I'm going butt naked,
tight ass.

55:25.723 --> 55:26.955
