55:45.976 --> 55:47.810
[laughing]

55:52.683 --> 55:54.550
BEYER: How are the girls?

55:54.552 --> 55:58.620
Good, yeah, except for Linda
not having a proper sendoff.

55:58.622 --> 56:00.856
