to keep in touch

56:05.963 --> 56:08.497
with your ex-patients, Sandra.

56:14.004 --> 56:16.038
Excellent work today
with the new girl.

56:16.040 --> 56:17.039
Standing and walking?

56:17.041 --> 56:18.974
BOTH: Amazing progress.

56:18.976 --> 56:21.543
SANDRA: Jinx!

56:21.545 --> 56:23.846
Forgot how hungry
being in the water makes you.

56:23.848 --> 56:25.781
