56:25.783 --> 56:27.716
And I'm fucking cold.

56:27.718 --> 56:29.651
I'm cold too.

56:53.477 --> 56:57.079
<i> ¶¶ [grand]</i>

57:12.096 --> 57:13.629
Where's Coffee?

