taking a massive

57:16.967 --> 57:19.601
Jack Palance-size dump.

57:19.603 --> 57:22.037
Have you noticed that
every time that man is here,

57:22.039 --> 57:24.106
every time he works,
our pipes are backed up?

57:24.108 --> 57:26.508
I mean, every single time.

57:26.510 --> 57:29.077
What are you doing
with a Taser?

57:30.981 --> 57:32.614
Fuck it, I'm going back.

57:32.616 --> 57:36.518
Whoa, Becky,
we came this far!

57:36.520 --> 57:38.887
